  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of AzaSite速 in Subjects With Blepharitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Center, Open-Label Study Evaluating the Cytokine and Eyelid Margin Bacterial Load Levels of Subjects Diagnosed With Chronic Blepharitis Following Dosing With AzaSite速 (Azithromycin Ophthalmic Solution) 1%</official_title>
  <sponsors>
