  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of AzaSite速 ophthalmic
      solution, 1% on signs &amp; symptoms of blepharitis and tear cytokine and eyelid bacterial load
      levels
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
